			<main>				
				<h2>Vice President, Communications &#038; Public Affairs (UK)</h2>
				<span class="date">August 5, 2022</span>
				
<div class="awsm-job-single-wrap awsm-job-form-plugin-style">

	
	
		<div class="awsm-job-content">
			
<div class="awsm-job-entry-content entry-content">
	
<h3>Description</h3>



<p>Bullpen Strategy Group (BSG) is a public affairs and strategic advisory firm that helps clients solve problems, grow, and manage risk.</p>



<p>We’re seeking an exceptional individual in a senior role to help build our public affairs and communications offering in the UK and Europe.</p>



<h3>Role</h3>



<p>The successful candidate will lead on building and developing BSG’s public affairs offering in the UK and<br>Europe. They will:</p>



<ul><li>Proactively seek out and develop new business opportunities for the firm.Plan and executive complex public affairs campaigns, integrating BSG’s research, media monitoring and digital capabilities where appropriate.</li><li>Lead the process of distilling obscure or technical information and transforming it into potent advocacy material.</li><li>Build comprehensive media plans, conduct press outreach, and lead on communications strategy for our clients.</li></ul>



<h3>Qualifications</h3>



<ul><li>A proven track record of working on UK or international public affairs campaigns.</li><li>A strong track record of pitching for and securing new business.</li><li>A minimum of 5 years of relevant experience is required, in a consultancy, campaigns or communications environment.</li></ul>



<h3>Other Desirable Skills</h3>



<ul><li>The ideal candidate possesses impeccable writing and editing skills, is comfortable working with journalists, demonstrates strong organizational skills, and approaches challenges with vigour and tenacity.</li><li>The ability to turn data, dense research materials and ideas into actionable next steps.</li><li>Strong writing skills, a professional demeanour, and good knowledge of both the national and international media environment.</li></ul>



<h3>Salary</h3>



<p>A competitive salary is available for the right hire, based on experience and qualifications. The remuneration package includes a generous commission on new business, private health insurance, and flexible working arrangements.</p>
</div><!-- .awsm-job-entry-content -->

<div class="awsm-job-specifications-container awsm_job_spec_below_content"><div class="awsm-job-specifications-row"></div></div>		</div><!-- .awsm-job-content -->

		<div class="awsm-job-form">
			
<div class="awsm-job-form-inner">

	
	<h2>
